wiki.summary: "Woman's World" is the lead single from Katy Perry’s upcoming sixth studio album, 143. It was released on July 11, 2024. On June 17, 2024, Perry announced via social media that she would be releasing a new single, "Woman's World", on July 11, 2024, followed the next day by a music video. The same day, she shared a short snippet of the song. This came after months of teasing new music and hinting at an upcoming sixth mainstream studio album. Read more on Last.fm.
